CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 22, 1941, pg. 8, reads: "Vesper Service Committee Prepares for Nov. 30th Meeting at 'Y' - Members of the Vesper Service Committee for the Dr. Howard Thurman Vesper Service being sponsored by the Centre Avenue Branch YWCA. The service will be held at Central Branch, 59 Chatham street on Sunday afternoon, November 30 at 4 o'clock.  Mrs. Alma A. Polk is chairman of the committee."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eighteen women, members of Vesper Service Committee, posed in YWCA
